---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of service for oriz - free online image tools."
>
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-8">Last updated: March 27, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          By using oriz, you agree to use these tools for lawful purposes. You may not:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Upload illegal, copyrighted, or harmful content</li>
          <li>Attempt to reverse engineer or exploit the service</li>
          <li>Use automated tools to abuse or overload the service</li>
          <li>Attempt to access data or systems you shouldn't</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">No Warranties</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">The service is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind.</strong> 
          We don't guarantee the service will be error-free, uninterrupted, or that results will meet your expectations.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">You own what you upload and create.</strong> 
          We don't claim ownership of your images. The oriz name, logo, and site design are our property.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We won't be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of this service.
          This includes lost profits, data loss, or costs of substitute services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We may update these terms occasionally. Continued use of the site means you accept any changes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-main)] mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Questions? Reach us at <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-main)]">contact@oriz.in</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>